            "Scores = QK^T / sqrt(4) → shape (3,3). scores[i][j] = how much token i attends to token j.",
            "Weights = softmax(scores, dim=-1) → each row sums to 1.",
            "Output = weights @ V → shape (3,4). Each token's output is a weighted mix of all values.",
