            "VQA with GPT-4V:\n  response = client.chat.completions.create(model='gpt-4-vision-preview',\n    messages=[{'role': 'user', 'content': [{'type': 'image_url', 'image_url': {'url': image_url}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': 'What is in this image? Describe in detail.'}]}])",
