            "Treating CLIP as a VQA model — CLIP embeds images and text but cannot generate text responses. For visual QA, use a full VLM like GPT-4V or LLaVA.",
            "Not providing sufficient context in the text prompt for multimodal reasoning — VLMs need guidance on what to analyze. 'Describe this image' is less effective than 'Identify all text visible in this image and list it verbatim.'",
