            "Highlight high correlations: high_corr = corr.where(np.triu(np.ones(corr.shape), k=1).astype(bool))\nhigh_corr_pairs = high_corr.stack().sort_values(ascending=False)\nprint('Most correlated pairs:', high_corr_pairs[high_corr_pairs.abs() > 0.7])",
