            "When to add a backend: the current static site is sufficient for: individual learners who use one device, anonymous learning without sync, and static content. A backend becomes necessary for: user accounts and authentication, progress that syncs across devices, personalized AI tutoring, community features (comments, study groups), and analytics.",
